            <title>[HADOOP-11154] Update BUILDING.txt to state that CMake 3.0 or newer is required on Mac.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-11154</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The native code can be built on Mac now, but CMake 3.0 or newer is required.  This differs from our minimum stated version of 2.6 in BUILDING.txt.  I&apos;d like to update BUILDING.txt to state that 3.0 or newer is required if building on Mac.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
