                            <comment id="14152463" author="cnauroth" created="Mon, 29 Sep 2014 22:52:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a trivial one-liner patch to update BUILDING.txt.  For reference, the reason for this is that earlier versions of CMake had a bug that prevented finding the JNI headers on Mac:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://public.kitware.com/Bug/bug_relationship_graph.php?bug_id=14508&amp;amp;graph=dependency&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://public.kitware.com/Bug/bug_relationship_graph.php?bug_id=14508&amp;amp;graph=dependency&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
