                            <comment id="14152508" author="hadoopqa" created="Mon, 29 Sep 2014 23:32:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;green&quot;&gt;+1 overall&lt;/font&gt;.  Here are the results of testing the latest attachment &lt;br/&gt;
